  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6568.73 sitting below the GEX flip at 6578 in a PIN regime, dealers are positioned to buy any dips toward the 6550 negative gamma wall while creating resistance on rallies above 6578-6580 where they'll aggressively sell delta. The massive positive gamma wall at 6580 (73B) should act as a magnet, creating strong mean-reversion dynamics that keep price range-bound between 6550-6580. Watch for dealers to provide liquidity on both sides but with heavier selling pressure emerging if we push through 6578, making the 6580 strike the key battleground level.",
